  },
  {
    question: "Is there an extra charge for same-day cleaning?",
    answer:
      "No rush fees or emergency charges - ever. Same-day cleaning in Huntsville is priced the same as our regular services. We believe urgent needs shouldn't come with penalty pricing.",
  },
  {
    question: "How quickly can you arrive in Huntsville?",
    answer:
      "Depending on availability and your location in Madison County, we can often arrive within 2-4 hours. Morning calls typically have the best availability for same-day service.",
  },
  {
    question: "What if I need cleaning for unexpected guests?",
    answer:
      "Call us immediately at 256-826-1100! Unexpected guests are one of the most common reasons for same-day requests. We understand the importance of having a clean, welcoming home and will get you guest-ready quickly.",
  },
  {
    question: "Do you offer same-day cleaning for home showings?",
    answer:
      "Yes! We work with Huntsville area realtors and homeowners to prepare properties for showings on short notice. A clean, polished home makes a significant difference in buyer impressions.",
  },
  {
    question: "What areas do you cover for same-day service?",
    answer:
      "We offer same-day service throughout Huntsville and Madison County including downtown Huntsville, East Huntsville, West Huntsville, Tanner, Elkmont, Ardmore, Belle Mina, and surrounding areas.",
  },
  {
    question: "What types of cleaning can you do same-day?",
    answer:
      "We can perform any type of cleaning same-day: regular cleaning, deep cleaning, move-out cleaning, party cleanup, pre-event preparation, or post-construction cleaning. Just tell us what you need.",
  },
  {
    question: "What if same-day isn't available?",
    answer:
      "If we can't accommodate same-day, we'll offer the next available slot - often next-day service. We prioritize urgent Huntsville requests and will find a solution that works for you.",
  },
  {
    question: "Can you handle same-day cleaning for aerospace or defense contractor visits in Huntsville?",
    answer:
      "Yes — Huntsville's defense and aerospace community regularly needs same-day cleaning for unexpected executive visits, impromptu client meetings at home offices, and the rapid-response hospitality that comes with the professional culture around Redstone Arsenal and Cummings Research Park. We understand the professional context and respond with the speed and discretion these situations require. Call 256-826-1100 as early as possible on the day you need service.",
  },
  {
    question: "Do you offer same-day cleaning for Hampton Cove and The Ledges luxury homes?",
    answer:
      "Yes — same-day service extends throughout Huntsville's premium communities including Hampton Cove, The Ledges, Monte Sano, Jones Valley, and Providence. Larger homes in these communities may require more time, so earlier same-day requests are always easier to accommodate for larger properties. We bring appropriately sized teams to handle larger homes within your timeframe when possible. Call to check availability and describe your home's size so we can staff accordingly.",
  },
  {
    question: "Can I request same-day cleaning after a party or event?",
    answer:
      "Absolutely — post-event same-day cleaning is one of our most common urgent requests in Huntsville. Whether last night's dinner party ran longer than expected or this morning's gathering left more cleanup than you anticipated, we can often respond within hours to restore your home. The sooner you call after the event, the better our chances of fitting you into the same day. Morning calls have the best availability even for same-day afternoon service.",
  },
  {
    question: "Is same-day cleaning available in Madison and other Madison County cities?",
    answer:
      "Yes — same-day service coverage extends throughout Madison County including Madison, Harvest, Meridianville, Owens Cross Roads, and surrounding communities. Distance and traffic routing can affect our exact response time to addresses further from central Huntsville, so call early and give us your location when you reach out. We cover the full county and will give you an honest estimate of our arrival time for your specific address.",
  },
];

const faqSchema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  mainEntity: faqs.map((faq) => ({
    "@type": "Question",
    name: faq.question,
    acceptedAnswer: {
      "@type": "Answer",
      text: faq.answer,
    },
  })),
};
import BookingCTA from "../../../components/BookingCTA.astro";
---

